metadata.name: Reformulated 1/1
metadata.description:
A virtual extension through the accelerating lexicon. Between the real and hyperreal an unwitting simulacrum, a deliberate distraction within rude awakenings. Seduced by the allure of the blue light glow. Delectable style. Vibrant shades of burnt orange, reflective black, multi-layer thick gold chain curb link chokers. A loose cotton strapless crop top, geometric bandana and ultra high waisted leather ruffle mini skirt. 

Synth Graph: a center front view portrait, 2012, photograph of a beautiful tanned female model a short black leather skirt, with a red spotted bandana tying back her hair, black high top sneakers, bright orange socks, red lipstick, walking down manhattan in the 2000s in early autumn, highly detailed. Sampler: klms, steps: 75, scale: 13.
